  "title": "Projects & Reporting - UAT Assistant (Up to $2800) #NKA",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: </strong>Geylang Bahru/Potong Pasir<br /></p><p><strong>Duration:</strong> Till September 2026<br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong>Mon - Fri, 8:30 - 6<br /></p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>Up to $2800 + pro-rated bonus upon completion<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Liaison person to communicate updates, information, and changes with internal stakeholders on project updates and progress</li><li>Provide support and assist Manager with project documentation, planning, requirement gathering, test scripting, project timeline tracking, etc.</li><li>Perform User Acceptance Testing and Quality assurance for new features on digital channels</li><li>Work closely and support technical teams to resolve identified issues </li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma with at least 1 year of relevant work experience in project management support role</li><li>Familiar e-services implementation on digital channels (web, app and kiosk)</li><li>Ability to multitask, well organised, eye for details</li><li>Self-starter, able to work independently while being a cohesive team member</li></ul><p><br />Ally<br />The Outsourcing Team<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA: 99C4599</p>",
